  "title": "SOLUTIONS CUSTOMER SERVICE ASSISTANT-SD",
  "description": "<p>JOB DESCRIPTION:</p><p>•\tCo-ordinate the order treatment with appropriate Solution Sales, Account Managers, Project Manager, Sales Operation, and Finance department.</p><p>•\tResponsible for generating orders and invoices</p><p>•\tResponsible for processing Credit Note</p><p>•\tAssist in administrative duties</p><p>•\tOther duties assigned by superior</p><p>MAIN RESPONSIBILITIES</p><p>•\tScope: ASIA regions</p><p>•\tMain interface with sales, finance and project management during order treatment process.</p><p>•\tFollow up with Sales on PO to be receive</p><p>•\tOrganize kick off meeting (Engagement Review) at purchase order reception for projects with all solution actors: Project Manager, Sales and Finance (Oracle Engagement reviews)</p><p>•\tPO Booking in Oracle and tracking list & follow-up projects till invoicing</p><p>•\tSupport on Risk Order entry in system</p><p>•\tSupport the credit management on customers' overdue treatment with Sales & Finance team</p><p>•\tSupport the financial controller on quarterly PO booking consolidation</p><p>•\tAssist on monthly PO booking and billing data extraction and cross check with manual data</p><p>•\tAssist on tracking for transaction fee order management</p><p>•\tAssist on documents storage in local shared folder, arrangement for courier service on invoicing documents</p><p>•\tCollaboration with cross team / BU on order management process</p><p>QUALIFICATIONS</p><p>Education & Experience</p><p>•\tMinimum Diploma</p><p>•\tAt least 2 years of relevant experience in backend customer service support</p><p>Skills</p><p>•\tSales administration and logistics (Letter of Credit, Payment Terms, Customs Rules…)</p><p>•\tSystem Tools : IT Literate (Microsoft Pack Office, …), Oracle & Microsoft Dynamic knowledge is a plus</p><p>•\tProficient in MS applications: Advanced Excel & Powerpoint</p><p>•\tProficient in Power BI</p><p>Personal abilities</p><p>•\tUse to work in complex administrative structures</p><p>•\tCustomer Service Oriented</p><p>•\tRigor & stress resistant</p><p>•\tAbility to work across various organizations in the group</p><p>•\tTeam player</p><p>•\tPro-active and good working attitude</p><p>•\tGood at interpersonal-& intercultural communication</p>",
